            "content": "if the norm of the instance is null",
            "assertion": "assert receiverObjectID.getNorm1()==Double.NEGATIVE_INFINITY || receiverObjectID.getNorm()==0.0 || receiverObjectID.getNormSq()==0.0 || receiverObjectID.getNormInf()==Double.POSITIVE_INFINITY;",
